---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import ChatBotPreview from '../components/ChatBotPreview.astro'
import KnowledgeCardPreview from '../components/KnowledgeCardPreview.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  current="platform"
  title="MD1 Platform | Knowledge Bank and ChatBotSDK"
  description="See how MD1 captures, structures, verifies, and deploys manufacturing knowledge through the Knowledge Bank and MD1 ChatBotSDK."
>
  <section class="px-6 py-24 md:px-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="mono mb-6 text-xs font-medium text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.58)]">How MD1 Works</div>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl text-5xl font-normal leading-[1.05] md:text-7xl">Knowledge is captured,<br />structured, and deployed.</h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.62)]">Four steps that turn fragmented information and tacit expertise into a living, trusted knowledge base.</p>

      <div class="mt-16 grid border-y border-[var(--md1-border)] md:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="border-b border-[var(--md1-border)] py-8 md:border-b-0 md:border-r md:pr-6">
          <div class="mono mb-6 text-xs text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.58)]">Step 01</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Ingest & Structure</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.62)]">Point MD1 at your documents and systems. It turns them into structured, tagged knowledge cards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-[var(--md1-border)] py-8 md:border-b-0 md:border-r md:px-6">
          <div class="mono mb-6 text-xs text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.58)]">Step 02</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Elicit</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.62)]">It draws out the unwritten layer from experts by reacting to real knowledge, not asking them to start from a blank page.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-[var(--md1-border)] py-8 md:border-b-0 md:border-r md:px-6">
          <div class="mono mb-6 text-xs text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.58)]">Step 03</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Verify</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.62)]">Your people confirm, correct, and challenge. Every claim carries its source and a trust level.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:pl-6">
          <div class="mono mb-6 text-xs text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.58)]">Step 04</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Compound</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.62)]">It improves with every use and becomes trusted knowledge used by both your people and your machines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-[var(--md1-border)] px-6 py-24 md:px-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="mb-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <span class="mono text-sm text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.58)]">01 / Product</span>
        <span class="font-semibold">The Knowledge Bank</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="max-w-4xl text-4xl font-normal leading-tight md:text-5xl">Start with one process worth proving.</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.68)]">
          <p>A focused engagement on one well-documented, expert-rich area. We sit with your team, ingest your documentation, capture what is not written down, and stand up a living knowledge base in weeks.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-[var(--md1-ink)]">Discover · 1-2 weeks.</strong> We sit with your operators and find the knowledge worth capturing.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-[var(--md1-ink)]">Prove · 2-4 weeks.</strong> We ingest your documentation, populate the knowledge base, and work alongside your experts.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-[var(--md1-ink)]">Grow · ongoing.</strong> Broaden across processes and plants. The knowledge base compounds as your people use it.</p>
        </div>
        <KnowledgeCardPreview />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-[var(--md1-border)] px-6 py-24 md:px-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="mb-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <span class="mono text-sm text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.58)]">02 / Product</span>
        <span class="font-semibold">MD1 ChatBotSDK</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="max-w-4xl text-4xl font-normal leading-tight md:text-5xl">Already deploying AI assistants?</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[rgba(18,35,58,0.68)]">
          <p>Most plants are, and they have no idea what those assistants are getting wrong, or what knowledge operators reveal while using them.</p>
          <p>The MD1 ChatBotSDK sits inside the chatbot you already run. It shows you where it fails, sharpens the sources it pulls from, and captures what your experts say in the gaps.</p>
          <p class="italic text-[var(--md1-ink)]">Sits on top of what you have. Your data never leaves your control.</p>
        </div>
        <ChatBotPreview />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
